data.description: Introducing a peaceful cul-de-sac home in Moreno Valley Ranch. This spacious home boasts an inviting double door entry, a fireplace, three bedrooms, three bathrooms, and a bonus room that can easily be converted into a fourth bedroom or used as an office space. The conveniently located primary suite downstairs features a double sink, walk-in closet, separate shower, and a jetted tub. Additionally, this home offers a large open living room, a large kitchen open to the family room with a kitchen island, and a generous backyard, perfect for entertaining. Enjoy the fantastic amenities offered by the association, including a pool, spa, exercise room, tennis/sport court, clubhouse, and BBQ area.
